@page "/components/confetti"
@using RizzyUI

<PageTitle>Confetti</PageTitle>

<RzQuickReferenceContainer>
    <RzArticle ProseWidth="ProseWidth.UltraWide">
        <SideContent>
            <RzQuickReference />
        </SideContent>
        <MainContent>
            <RzBreadcrumb class="mb-4 not-prose">
                <BreadcrumbList>
                    <BreadcrumbItem><BreadcrumbLink Href="/" hx-boost="true" hx-select="#content" hx-target="#content" hx-swap="outerHTML">Docs</BreadcrumbLink></BreadcrumbItem>
                    <BreadcrumbSeparator />
                    <BreadcrumbItem><BreadcrumbLink Href="/components" hx-boost="true" hx-select="#content" hx-target="#content" hx-swap="outerHTML">Components</BreadcrumbLink></BreadcrumbItem>
                    <BreadcrumbSeparator />
                    <BreadcrumbItem><BreadcrumbPage>Confetti</BreadcrumbPage></BreadcrumbItem>
                </BreadcrumbList>
            </RzBreadcrumb>

            <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H1" QuickReferenceTitle="Confetti" class="scroll-mt-20">Confetti</RzHeading>
            <RzParagraph>
                <code>RzConfetti</code> provides a canvas-backed celebration host, and <code>ConfettiTrigger</code> emits trigger contracts that run particle effects through Alpine without requiring Blazor interactivity.
            </RzParagraph>

            <RzAlert Variant="ThemeVariant.Information" class="not-prose my-6">
                <AlertTitle>Under the Hood</AlertTitle>
                <AlertDescription>
                    Each host registers itself by <code>data-confetti-host</code>. Delegated listeners resolve trigger events to a host by nearest ancestor or explicit <code>TargetId</code> and run the selected pattern.
                </AlertDescription>
            </RzAlert>

            <section class="my-8 py-2">
                <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H2" QuickReferenceTitle="Confetti Demo" class="scroll-mt-20">Confetti Demo</RzHeading>
                <RzParagraph>Hover the trigger to fire a burst over decorative hero text.</RzParagraph>
                <div class="not-prose relative my-6 rounded-lg border bg-card p-8">
                    <RzConfetti ManualStart="true" class="min-h-[24rem] rounded-md border bg-background p-8">
                        <div class="pointer-events-none bg-linear-to-b from-black to-gray-300/80 bg-clip-text text-center text-7xl font-semibold text-transparent dark:from-white dark:to-slate-900/10">Confetti</div>
                        <div class="mt-10 flex justify-center">
                            <ConfettiTrigger Trigger="ConfettiTriggerEvent.MouseEnter" Pattern="ConfettiPattern.Burst">
                                Hover for Confetti
                            </ConfettiTrigger>
                        </div>
                    </RzConfetti>
                </div>
                <RzCodeViewer Language="@CodeLanguage.Razor" class="mb-10">
&lt;RzConfetti ManualStart=&quot;true&quot;&gt;
    &lt;ConfettiTrigger Trigger=&quot;ConfettiTriggerEvent.MouseEnter&quot;&gt;
        Hover for Confetti
    &lt;/ConfettiTrigger&gt;
&lt;/RzConfetti&gt;
                </RzCodeViewer>
            </section>

            <section class="my-8 py-2">
                <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H2" QuickReferenceTitle="Basic Cannon" class="scroll-mt-20">Basic Cannon</RzHeading>
                <RzParagraph>Click the button to fire a centered burst that renders across the viewport (not clipped to the demo card).</RzParagraph>
                <div class="not-prose my-6 rounded-lg border bg-card p-8">
                    <RzConfetti Id="confetti-basic-viewport" ManualStart="true" class="fixed inset-0 z-40 overflow-visible" />
                    <ConfettiTrigger TargetId="confetti-basic-viewport" AsChild="true"><RzButton>Confetti 🎉</RzButton></ConfettiTrigger>
                </div>
                <RzCodeViewer Language="@CodeLanguage.Razor" class="mb-10">
&lt;RzConfetti Id=&quot;confetti-basic-viewport&quot; ManualStart=&quot;true&quot; class=&quot;fixed inset-0 overflow-visible&quot; /&gt;
&lt;ConfettiTrigger TargetId=&quot;confetti-basic-viewport&quot; AsChild=&quot;true&quot;&gt;
    &lt;RzButton&gt;Confetti 🎉&lt;/RzButton&gt;
&lt;/ConfettiTrigger&gt;
                </RzCodeViewer>
            </section>

            <section class="my-8 py-2">
                <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H2" QuickReferenceTitle="Random Direction" class="scroll-mt-20">Random Direction</RzHeading>
                <RzParagraph>Each click emits a burst with a randomized launch angle across the viewport.</RzParagraph>
                <div class="not-prose my-6 rounded-lg border bg-card p-8">
                    <RzConfetti Id="confetti-random-viewport" ManualStart="true" class="fixed inset-0 z-40 overflow-visible" />
                    <ConfettiTrigger TargetId="confetti-random-viewport" Pattern="ConfettiPattern.RandomDirection" AsChild="true"><RzButton>Random Confetti 🎉</RzButton></ConfettiTrigger>
                </div>
                <RzCodeViewer Language="@CodeLanguage.Razor" class="mb-10">
&lt;RzConfetti Id=&quot;confetti-random-viewport&quot; ManualStart=&quot;true&quot; class=&quot;fixed inset-0 overflow-visible&quot; /&gt;
&lt;ConfettiTrigger TargetId=&quot;confetti-random-viewport&quot; Pattern=&quot;ConfettiPattern.RandomDirection&quot; AsChild=&quot;true&quot;&gt;
    &lt;RzButton&gt;Random Confetti 🎉&lt;/RzButton&gt;
&lt;/ConfettiTrigger&gt;
                </RzCodeViewer>
            </section>

            <section class="my-8 py-2">
                <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H2" QuickReferenceTitle="Fireworks" class="scroll-mt-20">Fireworks</RzHeading>
                <RzParagraph>Runs a timed two-origin sequence that fills the viewport like fireworks.</RzParagraph>
                <div class="not-prose my-6 rounded-lg border bg-card p-8">
                    <RzConfetti Id="confetti-fireworks-viewport" ManualStart="true" class="fixed inset-0 z-40 overflow-visible" />
                    <ConfettiTrigger TargetId="confetti-fireworks-viewport" Pattern="ConfettiPattern.Fireworks" AsChild="true"><RzButton>Trigger Fireworks</RzButton></ConfettiTrigger>
                </div>
                <RzCodeViewer Language="@CodeLanguage.Razor" class="mb-10">
&lt;RzConfetti Id=&quot;confetti-fireworks-viewport&quot; ManualStart=&quot;true&quot; class=&quot;fixed inset-0 overflow-visible&quot; /&gt;
&lt;ConfettiTrigger TargetId=&quot;confetti-fireworks-viewport&quot; Pattern=&quot;ConfettiPattern.Fireworks&quot; AsChild=&quot;true&quot;&gt;
    &lt;RzButton&gt;Trigger Fireworks&lt;/RzButton&gt;
&lt;/ConfettiTrigger&gt;
                </RzCodeViewer>
            </section>

            <section class="my-8 py-2">
                <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H2" QuickReferenceTitle="Stars" class="scroll-mt-20">Stars</RzHeading>
                <RzParagraph>Launches layered star and circle particles with warm colors across the viewport.</RzParagraph>
                <div class="not-prose my-6 rounded-lg border bg-card p-8">
                    <RzConfetti Id="confetti-stars-viewport" ManualStart="true" Pattern="ConfettiPattern.Stars" class="fixed inset-0 z-40 overflow-visible" />
                    <ConfettiTrigger TargetId="confetti-stars-viewport" Pattern="ConfettiPattern.Stars" AsChild="true"><RzButton>Trigger Stars</RzButton></ConfettiTrigger>
                </div>
                <RzCodeViewer Language="@CodeLanguage.Razor" class="mb-10">
&lt;RzConfetti Id=&quot;confetti-stars-viewport&quot; ManualStart=&quot;true&quot; class=&quot;fixed inset-0 overflow-visible&quot; /&gt;
&lt;ConfettiTrigger TargetId=&quot;confetti-stars-viewport&quot; Pattern=&quot;ConfettiPattern.Stars&quot; AsChild=&quot;true&quot;&gt;
    &lt;RzButton&gt;Trigger Stars&lt;/RzButton&gt;
&lt;/ConfettiTrigger&gt;
                </RzCodeViewer>
            </section>

            <section class="my-8 py-2">
                <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H2" QuickReferenceTitle="Side Cannons" class="scroll-mt-20">Side Cannons</RzHeading>
                <RzParagraph>Emits mirrored side-cannon streams from the viewport edges.</RzParagraph>
                <div class="not-prose my-6 rounded-lg border bg-card p-8">
                    <RzConfetti Id="confetti-side-viewport" ManualStart="true" class="fixed inset-0 z-40 overflow-visible" />
                    <ConfettiTrigger TargetId="confetti-side-viewport" Pattern="ConfettiPattern.SideCannons" AsChild="true"><RzButton>Trigger Side Cannons</RzButton></ConfettiTrigger>
                </div>
                <RzCodeViewer Language="@CodeLanguage.Razor" class="mb-10">
&lt;RzConfetti Id=&quot;confetti-side-viewport&quot; ManualStart=&quot;true&quot; class=&quot;fixed inset-0 overflow-visible&quot; /&gt;
&lt;ConfettiTrigger TargetId=&quot;confetti-side-viewport&quot; Pattern=&quot;ConfettiPattern.SideCannons&quot; AsChild=&quot;true&quot;&gt;
    &lt;RzButton&gt;Trigger Side Cannons&lt;/RzButton&gt;
&lt;/ConfettiTrigger&gt;
                </RzCodeViewer>
            </section>

            <section class="my-8 py-2">
                <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H2" QuickReferenceTitle="Custom Shapes" class="scroll-mt-20">Custom Shapes</RzHeading>
                <RzParagraph>Uses path-based shapes for a varied celebratory pattern across the viewport.</RzParagraph>
                <div class="not-prose my-6 rounded-lg border bg-card p-8">
                    <RzConfetti Id="confetti-shapes-viewport" ManualStart="true" class="fixed inset-0 z-40 overflow-visible" />
                    <ConfettiTrigger TargetId="confetti-shapes-viewport" Pattern="ConfettiPattern.CustomShapes" AsChild="true"><RzButton>Trigger Shapes</RzButton></ConfettiTrigger>
                </div>
                <RzCodeViewer Language="@CodeLanguage.Razor" class="mb-10">
&lt;RzConfetti Id=&quot;confetti-shapes-viewport&quot; ManualStart=&quot;true&quot; class=&quot;fixed inset-0 overflow-visible&quot; /&gt;
&lt;ConfettiTrigger TargetId=&quot;confetti-shapes-viewport&quot; Pattern=&quot;ConfettiPattern.CustomShapes&quot; AsChild=&quot;true&quot;&gt;
    &lt;RzButton&gt;Trigger Shapes&lt;/RzButton&gt;
&lt;/ConfettiTrigger&gt;
                </RzCodeViewer>
            </section>

            <section class="my-8 py-2">
                <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H2" QuickReferenceTitle="Emoji" class="scroll-mt-20">Emoji</RzHeading>
                <RzParagraph>Fires emoji-based particles with secondary circle bursts across the viewport.</RzParagraph>
                <div class="not-prose my-6 rounded-lg border bg-card p-8">
                    <RzConfetti Id="confetti-emoji-viewport" ManualStart="true" class="fixed inset-0 z-40 overflow-visible" />
                    <ConfettiTrigger TargetId="confetti-emoji-viewport" Pattern="ConfettiPattern.Emoji" AsChild="true"><RzButton>Trigger Emoji</RzButton></ConfettiTrigger>
                </div>
                <RzCodeViewer Language="@CodeLanguage.Razor" class="mb-10">
&lt;RzConfetti Id=&quot;confetti-emoji-viewport&quot; ManualStart=&quot;true&quot; class=&quot;fixed inset-0 overflow-visible&quot; /&gt;
&lt;ConfettiTrigger TargetId=&quot;confetti-emoji-viewport&quot; Pattern=&quot;ConfettiPattern.Emoji&quot; AsChild=&quot;true&quot;&gt;
    &lt;RzButton&gt;Trigger Emoji&lt;/RzButton&gt;
&lt;/ConfettiTrigger&gt;
                </RzCodeViewer>
            </section>

            <section class="my-8 py-2">
                <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H2" QuickReferenceTitle="Component Parameters" class="scroll-mt-20">Component Parameters</RzHeading>

                <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H3" class="mt-6">RzConfetti</RzHeading>
                <div class="not-prose mt-6 mb-10 overflow-hidden rounded-md border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800">
                    <table class="w-full text-sm"><thead class="text-left bg-zinc-100/75 font-semibold text-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-900/50 dark:text-zinc-300"><tr><th class="px-4 py-3">Property</th><th class="px-4 py-3">Description</th><th class="px-4 py-3">Type</th><th class="px-4 py-3">Default</th></tr></thead><tbody class="divide-y divide-zinc-200 dark:divide-zinc-800">
                        <tr><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>ChildContent</code></td><td class="px-4 py-3">Visible content rendered above the confetti canvas.</td><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>RenderFragment?</code></td><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>null</code></td></tr>
                        <tr><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>Options</code></td><td class="px-4 py-3">Default fire request merged with trigger-level overrides.</td><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>ConfettiRequest?</code></td><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>null</code></td></tr>
                        <tr><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>GlobalOptions</code></td><td class="px-4 py-3">Canvas instance creation options.</td><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>ConfettiGlobalOptions?</code></td><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>{ Resize=true, UseWorker=true }</code></td></tr>
                        <tr><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>ManualStart</code></td><td class="px-4 py-3">When true, host waits for triggers instead of auto-firing on init.</td><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>bool</code></td><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>false</code></td></tr>
                        <tr><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>Pattern</code></td><td class="px-4 py-3">Default pattern used for auto-fire and unresolved trigger pattern.</td><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>ConfettiPattern</code></td><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>Burst</code></td></tr>
                        <tr><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>RespectReducedMotion</code></td><td class="px-4 py-3">Suppresses effects when reduced motion is preferred.</td><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>bool</code></td><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>true</code></td></tr>
                        <tr><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>HostId</code></td><td class="px-4 py-3">Optional logical host key for external targeting.</td><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>string?</code></td><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>null</code></td></tr>
                    </tbody></table>
                </div>

                <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H3" class="mt-6">ConfettiTrigger</RzHeading>
                <div class="not-prose mt-6 mb-10 overflow-hidden rounded-md border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800">
                    <table class="w-full text-sm"><thead class="text-left bg-zinc-100/75 font-semibold text-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-900/50 dark:text-zinc-300"><tr><th class="px-4 py-3">Property</th><th class="px-4 py-3">Description</th><th class="px-4 py-3">Type</th><th class="px-4 py-3">Default</th></tr></thead><tbody class="divide-y divide-zinc-200 dark:divide-zinc-800">
                        <tr><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>ChildContent</code></td><td class="px-4 py-3">Visible trigger content.</td><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>RenderFragment?</code></td><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>null</code></td></tr>
                        <tr><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>TargetId</code></td><td class="px-4 py-3">Explicit host target. If omitted, nearest host is used.</td><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>string?</code></td><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>null</code></td></tr>
                        <tr><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>Pattern</code></td><td class="px-4 py-3">Pattern override for the trigger event.</td><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>ConfettiPattern?</code></td><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>null</code></td></tr>
                        <tr><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>Options</code></td><td class="px-4 py-3">Request options merged with host defaults.</td><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>ConfettiRequest?</code></td><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>null</code></td></tr>
                        <tr><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>Trigger</code></td><td class="px-4 py-3">Event used to activate this trigger.</td><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>ConfettiTriggerEvent</code></td><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>Click</code></td></tr>
                        <tr><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>Disabled</code></td><td class="px-4 py-3">Prevents trigger activation and emits disabled semantics.</td><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>bool</code></td><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>false</code></td></tr>
                        <tr><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>AsChild</code></td><td class="px-4 py-3">Merges trigger attributes onto a child element.</td><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>bool</code></td><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>false</code></td></tr>
                        <tr><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>AriaLabel</code></td><td class="px-4 py-3">Optional accessible label for icon-only trigger content.</td><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>string?</code></td><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>null</code></td></tr>
                    </tbody></table>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="my-8 py-2">
                <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H2" QuickReferenceTitle="Supporting Types" class="scroll-mt-20">Supporting Types</RzHeading>
                <RzParagraph><code>ConfettiRequest</code> and <code>ConfettiGlobalOptions</code> contain serializable options sent through <code>data-*</code> attributes, and <code>ConfettiPattern</code>/<code>ConfettiTriggerEvent</code> define behavior selection.</RzParagraph>
            </section>

            <section class="my-8 py-2">
                <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H2" QuickReferenceTitle="Alpine API" class="scroll-mt-20">Alpine API</RzHeading>
                <RzParagraph>The host uses Alpine component <code>rzConfetti</code>.</RzParagraph>
                <div class="not-prose mt-6 mb-10 overflow-hidden rounded-md border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800">
                    <table class="w-full text-sm"><thead class="text-left bg-zinc-100/75 font-semibold text-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-900/50 dark:text-zinc-300"><tr><th class="px-4 py-3">Method</th><th class="px-4 py-3">Description</th></tr></thead><tbody class="divide-y divide-zinc-200 dark:divide-zinc-800">
                        <tr><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>fire(request)</code></td><td class="px-4 py-3">Fires one request after host/request merge and reduced-motion checks.</td></tr>
                        <tr><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>runPattern(pattern, request)</code></td><td class="px-4 py-3">Runs a named pattern including fireworks, side-cannons, stars, custom-shapes, and emoji.</td></tr>
                        <tr><td class="px-4 py-3"><code>reset()</code></td><td class="px-4 py-3">Clears active timers/frames and resets the confetti instance.</td></tr>
                    </tbody></table>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="my-8 py-2">
                <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H2" QuickReferenceTitle="Interoperability Notes" class="scroll-mt-20">Interoperability Notes</RzHeading>
                <RzParagraph>
                    Triggers without <code>TargetId</code> resolve to the nearest ancestor host. Use a stable explicit ID for decoupled layouts where trigger and host are not nested together.
                </RzParagraph>
            </section>
        </MainContent>
    </RzArticle>
</RzQuickReferenceContainer>
